{"word":"καταστρώννυμι","slug":"καταστρώννυμι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>καταστρώννυμι</b></el> <el>(and <el>-ύω</el>) (<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-στρώσω</el>) (aor1 <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>pass.</a></a> <el>-εστρώθην</el>) </el><p/><i>to lay low</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <el>κατέστρωντο οἱ βάρβαροι</el> <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/><div class='li250'><b>B. </b><el>καταστορέννυμι</el><p/></div><el>(<a href='S:participle'>part.</a> <a href='S:feminine'>fem.</a> <el>καστορνῦσα</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:participle'>part.</a> <a href='S:feminine'>fem.</a> <el>καστορνῦσα</el> as if from <el>καταστόρνυμι</el>\n<el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-στορέσω</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to over-spread</i> or <i>cover with</i> a thing, <el>τί τινι</el> <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to spread upon</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>III. </b><i>to throw down, lay low</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>; <el>καταστ. κύματα</el>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>sternere aequor</el>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}